ought to pass.
AN ACT CONCERNING OVERSIGHT OF MEDICAL CARE FOR
PERSONS WHO ARE INCARCERATED AT THE DEPARTMENT OF
CORRECTION.
Be it enacted by the Senate and House of Representatives in General
Assembly convened:
1 Section 1. Section 18-81pp of the 2026 supplement to the general
2 statutes is repealed and the following is substituted in lieu thereof
3 (Effective October 1, 2026):
